●	Principal: Dr. K. V. N. Sunitha
Principal — Profile (Dr. K. V. N. Sunitha)
Dr. K. V. N. Sunitha holds a B.Tech in ECE from ANU, an M.Tech in CS from REC Warangal (1993), and a Ph.D in CSE from JNTU Hyderabad (2006). She has over 30 years of teaching experience and over 15 years of research experience, and has served as Founder Principal of BVRIT Hyderabad since August 2012. She has guided 20 Ph.D scholars, authored 5 text books, and published more than 185 papers and 7 patents; her research areas include Natural Language Processing, Speech Processing, and Network & Web Security. Her awards include the ISTE Best Computer Science Engineering Teacher Award (2008), the CSI Mumbai Distinguished Principal Award (2017), the Deewang Mehtha Women in Education Award (2017), the IEI Engineer of the Year Award (2019), and the ISTE Best Engineering College Principal in Telangana State Award (2019). She is a Fellow of the Institution of Engineers (India) and a Senior Member of IEEE.






