Research Areas / Faculty Domains
Faculty publish across department-aligned research areas including VLSI & Communications (ECE) and Computer Science & Engineering; individual faculty thrust areas, publications, and Ph.D supervision details are listed department-by-department on the college's Research pages rather than in one consolidated directory.
The college website does not publish a single combined 'faculty list' page with qualifications for every staff member; instead, each department (CSE, ECE, EEE, IT, CSE-AI&ML, BS&H) maintains its own faculty listing under '[Department] > Faculty' and '[Department] > About HOD'. This document adds the department-wise faculty strength, named HODs and notable faculty achievements found on the 'About the Department' pages, plus the Principal's full profile, in addition to the leadership, placement, and library staff named on general/administrative pages — without inventing details not present on the source pages.
